<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Shing) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シング</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shing</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エルレイン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Elraine</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行っちゃった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They've left.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それより、あの女の人は？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More importantly, who is this lady?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あのー、大丈夫ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um, are you alright?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ありがとうございます。
助かりました。
お二人とも、強いのですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Thank you very much. You've saved me.
The two of you are very strong, aren't you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え、それほどでもないですよ〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Ahaha... Not all that much.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>I put the laughter in because it's voice acting, but it's not part of the text. Can remove it if prefered.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それより、どうして追われてたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More important than that,
why were they chasing you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これだけ強ければ、必ず役にたちますね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This much strength will be of use.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ハァ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haa!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>きゃあああああー！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>KYAAAAAA!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク！　大丈夫！？
……コハク、ねぇコハク！
なんで！　なんで返事をしないんだ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku! Are you okay?!
...Kohaku! Hey, Kohaku!
Why?! Why aren't you answering me?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク、コハク……
ちくしょぉぉぉぉおー！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku... Kohaku...
DAMMIT!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>抵抗はおよしなさい。
“女の人に剣を向けちゃダメ”でしょう？
それに、彼女の命が惜しくないのですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't resist.
"You shouldn't point a sword at a woman", right?
Besides, does her life not matter to you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>な、どういうことだ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wha-What are you talking about?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふふふ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
